{"tid":877103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"婦人持刀闖幼園斬傷14學童　傳同老公嗌交後報復社會","createTime":"2018-10-26T05:59:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T08:01:54.000Z","uid":75969,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fb05196826f1fa350f010db53c194b1312d66c0f","tid":877103,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T05:59:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181026/photo/bkn-20181026112836020-1026_00952_001_01p.jpg?20181026134912\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181026%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181026112836020-1026_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20181026134912&h=37dcbb58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">多名幼童被斬傷送院，疑犯被警方制服帶走。（互聯網）<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n內地再驚傳血洗幼稚園案件，重慶一名婦人持菜刀闖入一個幼稚園，將14名學童斬傷，部分孩子傷勢嚴重。警方到場將她制服帶走時，婦人被多人圍攻追打腳踢，警方要圍成人牆，才能將婦人帶離現場。<br />\n<br />\n事發於早上9時許，地點為巴南區魚洞新世紀幼兒園。從網上流傳的短片可見，多名年幼學童血流披面，有孩子的大半邊臉部被斬傷，整件外套都染滿鮮血，令人看得撕心裂肺。<br />\n<br />\n有一名目擊者在微信朋友圈稱，當時學童跟老師做完早操返回課室，疑犯尾隨他們後揮刀亂砍，之後再跑出來追斬尚未回到課室的學童。目擊者又指，疑犯下手狠毒，朝孩子的臉、頭和頸上狂斬。<br />\n<br />\n另有消息指疑犯因與丈夫吵架，心生不忿下欲報復社會，遂拿刀衝向幼稚園斬人洩憤；又有人稱疑犯患有精神病，惟以上說法暫未獲警方證實。<br />\n<br />\n據重慶警方通報，疑犯為39歲的巴南區人劉某，她在幼稚園門口持菜刀行兇，導致做完早操返課室途中的14名學生受傷。學校保安和工作人員將疑犯制服，警方接報後也迅速趕到現場處置，將受傷孩子送醫救治。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181026/photo/bkn-20181026112836020-1026_00952_001_02p.jpg?20181026134912\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181026%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181026112836020-1026_00952_001_02p.jpg%3F20181026134912&h=6fc21270&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">警方通報14名學童被斬傷。（互聯網）<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181026/bkn-20181026112836020-1026_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181026%2Fbkn-20181026112836020-1026_00952_001.html&d=o9ODwADp1XMLi3ieOJp2czCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=ba824cf8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181026/bkn-20181026112836020-1026_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4dc9906fc36f57eb575722a7b1285559c1fc5b75","tid":877103,"uid":114275,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T06:06:56.000Z","msg":"斬城管啦屌 斬幼蝗做乜"},{"pid":"56e128271e0ae1c50da2ea990d758ee27522b0f9","tid":877103,"uid":2772,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"4dc9906fc36f57eb575722a7b1285559c1fc5b75","tid":877103,"uid":114275,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T06:06:56.000Z","msg":"斬城管啦屌 斬幼蝗做乜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T06:08:36.000Z","msg":"斬幼蝗冇錯<br />\n但係一隻都斬唔死就離撚哂譜"},{"pid":"3c048b95ef8c5e47d97f6144cfcfd695082df2af","tid":877103,"uid":85557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T06:19:16.000Z","msg":"顛婆正傳"},{"pid":"790f81ff02be469d88f4b2bde16470dad181f1a2","tid":877103,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T06:20:43.000Z","msg":"同老公嘈交就報復社會，呢d咩邏輯黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"010e954e5f36653623fff2d6fcdfbf68a34cf433","tid":877103,"uid":191762,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T06:20:46.000Z","msg":"原來中國,以為安安幼稚園翻版<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f5e42cf3227e0996e1e54950dcf517dc51dd00","tid":877103,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T06:20:49.000Z","msg":"報復社會就整炸彈衝去支共機構丫嘛"},{"pid":"d5ec8d5a2e95a71d0c26838aac7b7446b4c202a1","tid":877103,"uid":36178,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T06:23:13.000Z","msg":"見到支那幼蝗d仆街樣又真係好難忍唔到落手斬"},{"pid":"b2bb010ca0eda704ef68a8b9af3862a82cf4089f","tid":877103,"uid":182475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4dc9906fc36f57eb575722a7b1285559c1fc5b75","tid":877103,"uid":114275,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T06:06:56.000Z","msg":"斬城管啦屌 斬幼蝗做乜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:21:46.000Z","msg":"欺善怕惡"},{"pid":"8e6a9461a8c256768722ee6ac180604ac26ff528","tid":877103,"uid":582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:29:57.000Z","msg":"比人斬到塊面又死唔去，第時醜樣比人歧視又會報復社會了"},{"pid":"15d41485aff87864fbc1e1942f0723ee0cceb287","tid":877103,"uid":112404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:46:25.000Z","msg":"一個都斬唔死咁失敗？"},{"pid":"154c49d61c83a7c22a226f44b4767a267df31c26","tid":877103,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15d41485aff87864fbc1e1942f0723ee0cceb287","tid":877103,"uid":112404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:46:25.000Z","msg":"一個都斬唔死咁失敗？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T08:01:54.000Z","msg":"婦人KDA = 0:1:0"}]}